channel.title: [KERNEL]: machine is too slow to run this server!
channel.description:
When my server is on sometimes I get this message in my server window:
[KERNEL]: machine is too slow to run this server!
Everything is fine like players aren't logging out but what does it mean or do?

item.title: [KERNEL]: machine is too slow to run this server!
item.dc:creator: @tonypker13 tonypker13
item.description:
@tonypker13 wrote:

[quote=“kihomura, post:8, topic:246048”][quote author=Trigger* link=topic=322527.msg2548976#msg2548976 date=1227423329]
Kernel is the commander guy. Machine is the thing that runs on electricity. Is is a term in grammer. Too is a term in grammer. Slow means your fat. To is a term in grammer. This is a term in grammer. Server is a game.
[/quote]

Grammar, grammar, grammar, GRAMMAR.[/quote]
I don’t think I got the word you were trying to tell us. Could you post it again?
